533
00:51:47,671 --> 00:51:50,765
<i>- Why didn't you buy her ice cream?
- Do it yourself.</i>

534
00:51:51,041 --> 00:51:52,508
<i>Are you still mad?</i>

535
00:51:52,676 --> 00:51:55,304
