536
00:51:56,980 --> 00:51:57,947
<i>Are you having fun?</i>

537
00:52:02,786 --> 00:52:05,778
The fact she opened her eyes
doesn't mean a thing.

538
00:52:07,190 --> 00:52:09,624
The nurse said
it's a reflex.

539
