Wait...

546
00:52:35,452 --> 00:52:38,046
No, I'm really sorry.
Forgive me...

547
00:52:38,221 --> 00:52:40,246
Stop.
I'm sorry I yelled at you.

548
00:52:43,560 --> 00:52:45,528
<i>do you think
I don't know?</i>

549
00:52:45,729 --> 00:52:46,923
<i>Know what?</i>

550
00:52:47,631 --> 00:52:49,394
<i>Not in front of the child.</i>

551
00:52:51,434 --> 00:52:53,493
<i>Want to go
into the water, sweetie?</i>

552
00:53:00,810 --> 00:53:03,176
<i>Play nice.
Daddy's coming right back.</i>

553
00:53:21,998 --> 00:53:23,488
<i>Don't play dumb.</i>

554
00:53:27,237 --> 00:53:30,764
<i>How old is your new floozy?
20? 18?</i>

555
00:53:31,808 --> 00:53:33,332
<i>Batya's age?</i>

556
00:53:36,313 --> 00:53:37,337
