Go on, knock.

564
00:54:39,676 --> 00:54:42,668
My wife, Keren.
This is...

565
00:54:43,213 --> 00:54:44,271
I forgot...

566
00:54:44,414 --> 00:54:46,644
I never told you.

567
00:54:46,850 --> 00:54:47,908
Nice to meet you.

568
00:54:48,051 --> 00:54:49,348
Are we too early?

569
00:54:49,519 --> 00:54:51,453
No, I'm all packed.
Come in.

570
00:54:51,621 --> 00:54:53,680
I'll go get the suitcase
from our room.

571
00:54:57,093 --> 00:54:58,924
The towels are clean.

572
00:55:00,330 --> 00:55:02,798
Why did you agree
to switch rooms with us?

573
00:55:02,932 --> 00:55:04,490
I thought
it's what you wanted.

574
00:55:06,102 --> 00:55:08,036
- Did Michael ask you to?
- No.

575
00:55:08,238 --> 00:55:09,933
I felt it.

576
00:55:11,474 --> 00:55:13,203
You're very generous.

577
00:55:13,410 --> 00:55:14,399
No.

578
00:55:15,478 --> 00:55:18,811
There are just certain men
I can't resist.

579
00:55:19,382 --> 00:55:21,509
We got married
the day before yesterday.

580
00:55:21,818 --> 00:55:22,978
Congratulations.

581
00:55:24,954 --> 00:55:27,616
I heard it was
a lovely wedding.

582
00:55:32,128 --> 00:55:34,221
I want you to
stay away from him.

583
00:55:40,904 --> 00:55:43,668
You can see the sea
from the balcony.

584
00:55:45,742 --> 00:55:47,209
I shut the blinds.

585
00:55:49,379 --> 00:55:50,971
