It's physical theater.

678
01:05:42,738 --> 01:05:46,731
Physical, yes, but why do you have
to touch each other all the time?

679
01:05:48,811 --> 01:05:51,712
- You don't like touching at all.
- What?

680
01:05:52,548 --> 01:05:55,312
- Nothing, never mind.
